long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Helps to complete the work orders in hfc maximo. 
If you have access to nbn hfc maximo application this will help.
For those who do not have access to nbn internal domain it will not work.
The extension will help to reduce the over all time taken to perform this operation manually. 
Bulk option is also available.
This extension does not collect/store any personal information.
